The paper deals with channel estimation in millimeter wave (mmWave) MIMO systems, which is a topic of interest in the fields of information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), control theory (cs.SY), multimedia (cs.MM), and machine learning (cs.LG). However, given the focus on signal processing and estimation algorithms, cs.IT and cs.NI are the most likely categories.
